“You were 1 of 4, I’ve always been 1 of 1”

\- Britt Baker to Mercedes Monè

Britt Baker calls Mercedes out for changing. The crowd chants YOU SOLD OUT. Britt says she'll follow the rules and wait until Wembley. She won't touch Mercedes

But this b\*itch is getting on her nerves \*BONK\* Kamille catches a mic to the head and Britt splashes her onto Mercedes

Britt stands tall with the TBS title.

