*   ## **_KAZUCHIKA OKADA VS CLAUDIO CASTAGNOLI GOES TO A DRAW_**
    

After the match the Young Bucks say they would give us five more minutes but Okada's contract this week was for a twenty minutes match, NOT a twenty five.

They're going to jump Claudio when Darby and FTR come out to save him and set up the next match.

