![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9d13aedf-8447-4b76-9edc-7616908a0d04/20240821_185925.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_DARBY ALLIN AND FTR DEF. THE ELITE_**
    

Darby Allin pins Matt Jackson after a great six man to head into Wembley with all the momentum in the world.

After the match, the Acclaimed come out to say they haven't been forgetten about and they're leaving with the AEW Tag Team Championships in Sunday.

