![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f726a67e-3694-4d9f-a48e-f078914da65e/Screenshot_20240821_191318.jpg?format=original)

Swerve is out for the contract signing after being GLAZED by Nigel McGuinness during the introduction.

Swerve says Bryan won't be safe anywhere on Earth, even if he's with his family. Bryan comes out and immediately hits Swerve with the Busaiku Flying Knee.

Bryan says maybe it's because he doesn't cut 20 minute promos every week but Swerve must've forgotten Bryan is the best wrestler in the world and has been for the past twenty years.

Can Bryan Danielson win the world championship from Swere Strickland this Sunday?

The crowd says YES YES YES

